      <title>南非民意调查显示 ANC 选举支持率低于 40%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/south-african-poll-finds-anc-election-support-falling-below-40</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的民意调查显示，南非执政党非洲人国民大会的支持率已降至 40% 以下，距离该国举行选举还不到三个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/south-african-poll-finds-anc-election-support-falling-below-40</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 19:11:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
